00:20:25,375 --> 00:20:27,541
There's only one person
with moves like that!

485
00:20:27,625 --> 00:20:31,125
It's Razor Girl,
the "maid among maids!"

486
00:20:31,208 --> 00:20:34,833
[singing continues]

487
00:20:34,916 --> 00:20:36,291
Awesome!

488
00:20:36,375 --> 00:20:38,333
[BODYGUARD]
They're at 10 million views.

489
00:20:38,416 --> 00:20:41,375
Makina. Just so you're aware.

490
00:20:41,458 --> 00:20:43,291
They're streaming this
performance live

491
00:20:43,375 --> 00:20:45,458
and over 10 million people
from around the world

492
00:20:45,541 --> 00:20:47,208
are watching it as we speak.

493
00:20:47,291 --> 00:20:48,625
10 million?

494
00:20:48,708 --> 00:20:51,041
It's quite the
ironic twist, isn't it?

495
00:20:51,125 --> 00:20:52,750
Now if you were to expel her,

496
00:20:52,833 --> 00:20:54,833
it's more likely to hurt
the school's image.

497
00:20:54,916 --> 00:20:55,875
[gasps]

498
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:58,916
[MAKINA]
I don't understand.

499
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,333
I mean, why did
you take her side

500
00:21:01,416 --> 00:21:04,125
when I just wanted what
was best for the school?

501
00:21:04,208 --> 00:21:05,333
It's not like that.

502
00:21:05,416 --> 00:21:06,583
[gasps]

503
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:10,583
[laughs] I wasn't siding
with her or against you.

504
00:21:10,666 --> 00:21:13,208
But I will always side with
what is most amusing,

505
00:21:13,291 --> 00:21:15,958
and in this case, Mr.Kagami
was able to bring out

506
00:21:16,041 --> 00:21:18,083
something truly
interesting in her.

507
00:21:18,166 --> 00:21:19,583
In time, perhaps he can make

508
00:21:19,666 --> 00:21:22,041
this entire nation
shine as well.

509
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:27,166
And I'll be there
aiding his every step.

510
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:28,666
[MAKINA gasps]

511
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:33,708
[singing continues]

512
00:21:41,833 --> 00:21:44,250
And that concludes
